makeself - An utility to generate self-extractable archives.

Version 2.7.1 downloaded from:
    https://github.com/megastep/makeself/releases/download/release-2.7.1/makeself-2.7.1.run

Running the package extracts the files into a makeself-2.7.1 subdirectory.
This readme.tool was added to the directory.

Then following command was executed to apply the patch stored in the current version of this tool:
    patch -Np1 -i patch.diff

At last it was zipped up.
